name: Tifa's purple (refined) dress embedding by Corneo
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding trained on the purple dress worn by Tifa Lockhart in Final Fantasy VII Remake. Should be able to apply to other characters/designs with the right tags, though of course by itself it will lean towards creating characters that look like Tifa.

v2 example images produced with my 7th Heaven mix https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix. The embedding was trained on NAI so will work best with a NAI-based model.

Use corneo_tifa_dress to activate.

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!

modelVersions.description: An update as with my other existing embeds to fix a problem I had in my training data tagging, meaning the result is now more accurate. The dress should be more consistently designed than before, though it also makes it look more like Tifa on average than before.
